        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">If you're a pilot facing a crisis, you're not alone. Breathe Pilot is dedicated to providing support and assistance to pilots in times of need. We are a team of fellow pilots offering immediate help and guidance whenever you require it.  Where there is help, there is hope</p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
