  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-blue-100" id="how-we-help">
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row items-center py-20">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center">
        <img src="pilot-worried-stressed.webp" alt="pilot worried and stressed" class="lg:rounded-[100rem] lg:px-10 pt-20 lg:pt-0 object-cover">
      </div>
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl text-center pb-20 px-10">Immediate Support</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 tracking-tight max-w-lg px-10">
          Aviation is a demanding industry, and it's not uncommon to experience stress, anxiety, or other challenges along the way. Our crisis hotline is available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, staffed by aviation professionals that can understand the unique pressures and circumstances that pilots face. Whether you're struggling with job related stress, personal issues, or mental health concerns, our team is here to listen, provide support, and help you navigate through difficult times.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row-reverse items-center py-20">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center">
        <img src="pilot-on-the-phone.webp" alt="pilot on the phone" class="lg:rounded-[100rem] lg:px-10 pt-20 lg:pt-0 object-cover">
      </div>
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl text-center pb-20 px-10">Confidential and Non-Judgmental</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 tracking-tight max-w-lg px-10">
          At BreathePilot, we prioritize confidentiality and respect for your privacy. All calls to our crisis hotline are confidential, and our staff members are committed to providing non-judgmental support in a safe and understanding environment. You can feel comfortable reaching out to us knowing that your information will be kept confidential and that you will be treated with empathy and respect.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


